DarkMouse::
She saw they had returned back to the base and called out over the PA 
system. "Welcome home boys. Glad to see your all in one piece and not 
scrap metal."  She clicked off the system and sat back in the 
chair. "Yeah, just a desk jocky and nothing else for poor mouse 
here."  She took out her knife and cut her arm.  She watched the 
glowing mech fluid flow for a second, then the wound healed up 
perfectly. "Yeah," she put the blade away,"poor mouse."
